Package dashboard.readout

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ColorUpdatable
    Defines the functionality of a class that can be updated via a Color.
    ImageUpdatable
    Defines the functionality of a class that can be updated via a GImage.
    Incrementable
    Defines the functionality of a class that can be incremented and decremented.
    LevelUpdatable
    Defines the functionality of a class that can be set to various discretized levels.
    LocationUpdatable
    Defines the functionality of a class that can be updated via two GPoints.
    NumberUpdatable
    Defines the functionality of a class that can be updated via a double.
    StringUpdatable
    Defines the functionality of a class that can be updated via a String.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BarReadout
    Implements a Readout that represents a bar whose length scales linearly with input values.
    BarReadout.Builder
    Builder for the BarReadout class.
    BufferReadout
    Implements a Readout that represents a scrollable graphical buffer of text.
    BufferReadout.Builder
    Builder for the BufferReadout class.
    ColorReadout
    Implements a Readout that represents an LED status light.
    ColorReadout.Builder
    Builder for the ColorReadout class.
    CompassReadout
    Implements a Readout that represents a compass which always points in the direction of a user-specified goal.
    CompassReadout.Builder
    Builder for the CompassReadout class.
    DialReadout
    Implements a Readout that represents a dial whose angle scales linearly with input values.
    DialReadout.Builder
    Builder for the DialReadout class.
    ImageReadout
    Implements a Readout that represents a video screen.
    ImageReadout.Builder
    Builder for the ImageReadout class.
    LevelReadout
    Provides the base functionality for a Readout that has discretized levels.
    LevelReadout.Builder<T extends LevelReadout.Builder>
    Builder for the LevelReadout class, to be extended by all subclasses of LevelReadout.
    MinimapReadout
    Implements a Readout that represents a minimap with pins to mark various locations.
    MinimapReadout.Builder
    Builder for the MinimapReadout class.
    Readout
    Provides the base functionality for a graphical widget that can display data.
    Readout.Builder<T extends Readout.Builder>
    Builder for the Readout class, to be extended by all subclasses of Readout.
